com.undead_pixels.dungeon_bots.script

Class LuaScript

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.undead_pixels.dungeon_bots.script.LuaScript

  • public class LuaScript
extends java.lang.Object
    A LuaScript is an asynchronous wrapper around an execution context for a sandbox that is invoked using a LuaSandbox.
